@NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5182

### Health
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### Sources
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/sources

### News (paginated)
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?page=1&pageSize=10

### News with content only
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?page=1&pageSize=10&hasContent=true

### News detail
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news/{{newsId}}

### Enrich article content
POST {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news/{{newsId}}/enrich-content

### News rewrites (paginated)
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites?page=1&pageSize=20

### News rewrites for source news
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites?sourceNewsId={{newsId}}&page=1&pageSize=20

### News rewrite detail
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites/{{rewriteId}}

### Create news rewrite
POST {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceNewsId": "{{newsId}}",
  "title": "Переписанный заголовок",
  "summary": "Краткое описание",
  "content": "Полный переписанный текст новости."
}

### Update news rewrite
PUT {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites/{{rewriteId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Обновлённый заголовок",
  "summary": null,
  "content": "Обновлённый текст."
}

### Delete news rewrite
DELETE {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news-rewrites/{{rewriteId}}
